                                          Marvel Toys & Sets

                                          Build something extraordinary and become your favourite hero with LEGO® Marvel toys and playsets! Team up with other legendary Marvel characters, such as Iron Man, Thor, Spider-Man, Black Panther and many more, on daring missions to defeat super villains. Recreate epic film action scenes from the Avengers and other Marvel movies or create your own amazing adventures with cool minifigures, vehicles, buildings, gadgets and weapons. Discover great LEGO® Marvel sets for fans of all ages – perfect gifts for boys, girls and adults alike. Will good or evil triumph? The fate of the Marvel Universe is in your hands!
